headline: CEO Advisor, Inc. Advises Wyvern Technologies, Inc. on its Exit Strategy / Sale
summary: CEO Advisor, Inc. (www.CEOAdvisor.com), a Newport Beach, CA mergers and acquisitions and business advisory firm, has advised Wyvern Technologies, Inc., a leader in aerospace and defense electronics and technology components on its sale to Extant Aerospace, a TransDigm Corporation ("TransDigm") (NYSE:TDG), the global leader in lifecycle sustainment of aerospace and defense electronics.
